@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.sin(v1 + 0.28) - v1))
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.13 - v2 + 0.59)) / wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.52)))
    v0 = 0.09
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.03)) - ((tmp + 0.73 - v2 + 0.84) - wp.abs(v1 + 0.92)))
    v1 = wp.sin((v2 - (tmp + 0.16 / v1 + 0.59)))
    tmp = wp.cos((v1 + (tmp + 0.14 + v1 + 0.75)))
    v2 = 0.99
    data[tid] = v0
